{"tid":825248,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[三叔碌鳩爆炸] 過熱出煙，用戶起訴要求禁售","createTime":"2018-09-17T12:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T07:10:40.000Z","uid":48234,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa57375e8a33c71f99d763c9fefbc39df83a736c","tid":825248,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2Fgalaxy-note-9-explosion%2F&d=icry47PlOih8PFT35jB9t9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=87c0c0e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/09/17/galaxy-note-9-explosion/</a><br />\n<br />\n對於 Galaxy Note 7 的全球連環爆炸事件，引起全球航空禁攜機上飛機，最後全球回收，成為全球「最短命手機」，估計大家可能仍然心有餘悸。今年來到 Note 9，不幸的事又再發生，全球首宗 Note 9 意外在開賣後不足一個月就已經發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/252343243222343324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F252343243222343324.jpg&h=7296330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在紐約的 Diane Chung 當時正在皇后區 Bayside 公寓乘搭升降機，她發現手機有點熱，於是停止使用並放入手袋，之後手機開始發出刺耳的聲音並開始釋出濃煙。於是她快速拿出手機，並放到地上。Diane Chung表示當時極度恐慌，升降機內只有其一人，她立即按下升降機按鈕令，門打開後正好在公寓大堂，於是她快速把地上的手機踢出門口，一名路人幫忙用水澆熄手機。<br />\n<br />\n事件之後 Diane Chung 通過律師向 Samsung 提出訴訟，她認為 Samsung 應知 Note 9 有缺憾，要求 Samsung 賠償損失及提出銷售禁令。Samsung 回應「未收到涉及 Galaxy Note9 的類似事件的任何報告，我們正在調查此事。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Samsung 爆炸小檔案：</span><br />\n在 Galaxy Note 7 爆炸事件發生初期，Samsung 一直對外否認自身產品設計有問題，甚至有地區服務點認為是用戶自家使用不當引致，最後爆炸事件完全不能停止。Samsung 在輿論壓力下終全球回收。半年之後，Samsung 發表調查報告，終承認自身電池設計在製造過程中產生問題。全球回收超過250萬部。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 7 當時使用 3500mAh電池，而到了 Galaxy Note 8 Samsung 改用低一點的 3300mAh 電池，不過 Galaxy Note 9 卻是全系列最大電池 4000mAh。估計如果爆起來威力亦是歷來最強。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">早就估到碌柒爆炸完碌鳩都爆炸㗎啦<br />\n不過呢次爆幾多單呢?</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf3179f05f51a02f10313f62c409d0e42f9136f5","tid":825248,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fda48979c1e9ac91d3fb58d02decc27bc48bb0e","tid":825248,"uid":204306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"c7c9db05786abf4ad719a037218b506c67043cc2","tid":825248,"uid":92477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"我都見到伯母個窿出煙"},{"pid":"c8db05b44f2ecb77825100310f30eef66436072e","tid":825248,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"抵啦泡菜狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9d0a6f82617038215e0bff2defc7c55637c9ef","tid":825248,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"02725c0fc3b0b85ccdf407eb5b605b824b91d9a5","tid":825248,"uid":51080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"班An 狗又唔敢面對，話蘋果作新聞老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8565b4cbd3ac51b2cd7456a262fd53c4fef656","tid":825248,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"【Note 9來了】導入水冷黑科技　三星旗艦機Note 9電池可用一整天<br />\n<br />\n為了對抗新一代iPhone，三星也是卯盡全力，把最新技術放進Note 9之中，由於過去Note 7曾爆發電池爆炸事件，讓三星在上一代機種時，將電池容量調降，但這次三星導入了新型的碳纖維管水冷技術，不但擴大散熱管尺寸，更利用液體水冷技術，大幅提高散熱性。<br />\n<br />\n「靠著新的碳纖維水冷技術，讓新款Note 9能夠擁有更高效能的CPU與GPU，同時也加大了內存容量到512GB，當然最重要的電池容量，也跟著加大到4,000mAh，可以讓用戶使用一整天，都不需要充電。」台灣三星主管透露。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/amp/20180809fin015/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2Famp%2F20180809fin015%2F&d=icry47PlOih8PFT35jB9t9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9ad2d27c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/amp/20180809fin015/</a>"},{"pid":"1b8d246292f1e1245c32b408d2854e8fec2e451f","tid":825248,"uid":24853,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個傻閪fd同我講note9世界第一<br />\n爆炸就第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3548d2c47ea91ab2f73b9c2498693efc8c38a9f5","tid":825248,"uid":5490,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:00:24.000Z","msg":"碌柒又著火，碌鳩又著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa20418666c616afe0ebd34e642369b0a1e30b35","tid":825248,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"02725c0fc3b0b85ccdf407eb5b605b824b91d9a5","tid":825248,"uid":51080,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"班An 狗又唔敢面對，話蘋果作新聞老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:21:00.000Z","msg":"an你老母狗,咪撚一碌鳩打一船人<br />\n係三星狗"},{"pid":"2aa76b8557b29a50459c7f5ceb7eba2d38050154","tid":825248,"uid":136773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔怕生壞命最怕改壞名， note7完到 note 9  仲要賣到8000蚊"},{"pid":"c5e72b2b16e0a55fb33a4b89ac24afd58ee98b4a","tid":825248,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"恐怖份子或成最大嬴家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要大量購入了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3fbc34a45504bebda3cc6d31dcd75d2350310a","tid":825248,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n炸撚死班用samsu